  _lines:
  - Did he sppok ya, hon?
  - He certainly doesn't mean any of it.
  - I mean if you only knew half of what he'd been through...
  - Truly a terrible thing, to live without a mother's love.
  _playerReplyOptions:
  - Have you both known each other long?
  - I wouldn't say he SCARED me...
  - Know anyone else from around here?
